data.description: Welcome to 125 Jesse Ln, Walters, OK! This spacious and well-maintained 2018 Clayton manufactured home offers, a generous living apace of 2,052 sq ft and features 2 living areas, 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, presenting ample room for the whole family. Prepare to be impressed by the recent upgrades that enhance the comfort and convenience of this residence. The AC unit has been newly upgraded in 2022, ensuring optimal climate control throughout the year and providing a cool retreat during the hot summer months, large covered front & back porch, 2 exterior buildings (small shed has electricity) and a storm cellar! The siding of the property is currently being repaired, which will give the exterior a fresh and updated look. New gutters are scheduled to be installed, offering improved water management and protecting the overall structure of the home. Upon entry, you will be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere that flows throughout the open floor plan. The living area provides a cozy space to relax and unwind, while the well-appointed kitchen offers plenty of counter space, modern appliances, and ample cabinetry for all your storage needs. The bedrooms are generously sized and provide comfortable retreats for rest and relaxation, while the bathrooms offer both functionality and style. This home is situated on 5 acres (MOL) allowing ample opportunities to expand or start up your own farm while also offering a peaceful and friendly neighborhood atmosphere - Close proximity to schools, parks, and local amenities, ensures convenience for your everyday needs. Don't miss this opportunity to make this house your dream home. Schedule a viewing today and witness the exciting potential and charm this property has to offer! Listing Agent: Carrie Austin (580)512-6647.
